<cb:div type="nanchuan-notes">
<head>漢譯南傳大藏經 註解</head>
<p>
<note n="0253001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0253001">過去二十四佛之第八佛。Buddhavaṁsa 3l; Jātaka I, P, 36。</note>
<note n="0253002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0253002">讀為 upaṭṭhahiṁ（暹羅本）。</note>
<note n="0253003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0253003">Samalaṅkata（莊嚴）。</note>
<note n="0254001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0254001">在底本已將 āsiṁ-gopako 之連結符——除去。</note>
<note n="0254002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0254002">kanavera（or Kanavīra）屬夾竹桃。</note>
<note n="0255001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0255001">nāḷikera（椰子）。</note>
<note n="0255002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0255002">Indasama（帝似）。</note>
<note n="0256001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0256001">Gosujāta（牛善生）。</note>
<note n="0257001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0257001">讀為 ogāhayi（暹羅本）。</note>
<note n="0257002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0257002">Soṇṇābha（黃金光）。</note>
<note n="0257003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0257003">此處為 Kaṇikārapupphiya（伽尼伽拉花），但脚註及暹羅本皆與標題同。</note>
<note n="0258001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0258001">讀為 nāmāsi（暹羅本）。</note>
<note n="0258002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0258002">Samodaka（等水）。</note>
<note n="0259001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0259001">Samuddhara（濟出）。</note>
<note n="0260001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0260001">Parisuddha（清淨）。</note>
<note n="0260001-1" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0260001-1">Bandhumatī（親惠城）。</note>
<note n="0261002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0261002">Āveyya 暹羅本為 Āvela（花環），應予採用。</note>
<note n="0261001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0261001">讀為 nāmāsi（暹羅本）。</note>
<note n="0261002-1" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0261002-1">底本 appasādo va ramuddhe 暹羅本為 appasaddho ca……。</note>
<note n="0261003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0261003">[02]</note>
<note n="0262001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0262001">Māla（華鬘）指 Samādapaka 布施之華鬘。</note>
</p>
